<plot>This documentary treats movie fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of The Pianist, Roman Polanski's film about one man's struggle to survive in the ghetto of WWII Warsaw. Includes interviews with the cast and crew, who share some of their experiences with working on the movie, and discuss some of the efforts that it required.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?574167</url></doc>
